"During initialization, all ``userSetup.py`` on the path are called, but "
"``userSetup.mel`` is not called."

#: cymel.initmaya.initMaya:9 of
msgid "繰り返し呼び出しても問題はない。"
msgstr "There is no problem even if you call it repeatedly."

#: cymel.initmaya.initMaya:11 cymel.initmaya.isMayaInitialized:3 of
